data.description:
Back on the market.  No fault of the seller. This 3 bedroom 3 bath home has so much space.  If you are one that likes to entertain, this house definitely has what it takes.  Back yard is fenced and has a covered patio area.  Wood burning fireplace upstairs and downstairs however, the sellers have not used the fireplaces since they purchased the home.  Newer HVAC, water heater, roof, 200 amp service, flooring and some light fixtures. Stove, refrigerator, washer, dryer and treadmill in the basement stays and swing set stays outside.
Buyer to verify all MLS information including but not limited to square feet, measurements, lot size, features, exemptions/taxes, schools, etc.
